Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on May 30, 2025, the following bill was signed into law:
S.B. NO. 281, S.D. 1, RELATING TO TORTURE.
H.D. 2, C.D. 1 ACT 147
